{"type": "article", "id": 14856, "title": "ZENLET钱包", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-14T07:09:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607102448hJiSdPer5Ts76XHL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自台湾的设计团队 ZENLET 设计了这款钱包，外形有点像 iPhone 的手机壳，方正而极简。用指头划开时，所有的卡片呈现出有层次的排列，非常直观方便。钱包厚度 1 厘 米，可以承受一定的重量而不会毁坏里面的东西。另外，密封式设计及其防水功能再加上 RFID  ( Radio Frequency Identification，射频识别技术)可以安全保护里面的信用卡。这款钱包有多种颜色可选，目前刚刚完成众筹，即将进入预售阶段。<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1562350776/zenlet-amazingly-intuitive-wallet/description\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142255j2XbpGZ9leSEwthz.gif\" width=\"680\" height=\"255\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142257Yx51vCjRXdAhZ8Ii.jpg\" width=\"1063\" height=\"709\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66698024\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142257VIR2gM8rUZBsWwSq.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"952\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142258mOGl3MvdZnEeczfb.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"411\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60441176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}